content:
To provide user access to Einstein Discovery functionality, the CRM Analytics Plus license and Einstein Predictions license provide standard permission sets and permissions that you can assign to user accounts.

These two licenses provide identical permission sets:

*   **CRM Analytics Plus User**: Restricted access to use a model, including getting predictions and improvements derived from a model
*   **CRM Analytics Plus Admin**: Admin-level access to all Einstein Discovery features, including the ability to create and deploy models

The CRM Analytics Plus User permission set provides single-user access to read-only features enabled by the CRM Analytics Plus or Einstein Predictions license.

These include:

*   **Use Einstein Discovery**: Use Einstein Discovery and view the models that you have permission to view.
*   **View Einstein Discovery Recommendations**: View Einstein Discovery predictions, improvements, and related details that are derived from a deployed model.

The CRM Analytics Plus Admin permission set provides admin-level access to all features enabled by the CRM Analytics Plus or Einstein Predictions license.

These include:

*   **Can Deploy and Manage Einstein Discovery predictions**: Deploy and manage Einstein Discovery prediction definitions and models.
*   **Can Run Einstein Discovery for Reports**: Run Einstein Discovery analysis on reports.
*   **Create and Update Einstein Discovery Models**: Create models to discover relationships between a business relevant metric and the explanatory variables that are potential influencers of that metric.

Custom permission sets can be created to give users access to specific combinations of analytics functionality, including Einstein Discovery features.
title: Einstein Discovery Permission Sets and User Access
